182
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:17,880
But I can't risk it
blowing back on me. So--

183
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,320
It won't. I can promise you that.

184
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:25,800
I can bring you in
if you do something for me.

185
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,400
