186
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:31,920
Kiss me.

187
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,560
Tell me you love me.

188
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,600
Um...

189
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,320
That's really what you want?

190
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,720
