193
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,800
- I wish I was there.
- Oh, I know.

194
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:44,240
<i>On behalf of the Hexts,
the amusement park</i>

195
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,760
<i>is yours for the evening.
Our hosts eagerly await you</i>

196
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,480
