199
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:13,040
- Oh, wow.
- Wow!

200
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:16,800
You're here because
there is a secret among us.

201
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,200
And now,

202
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:21,760
at long last, the truth must...

203
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:25,480
The truth must...

204
