213
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,880
- Good.
- Very, very good.

214
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,400
Yes, yes.

215
00:14:55,520 --> 00:15:00,480
A most heinous crime has been
committed in this beloved amusement park.

216
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,200
